<% title 'MIAM not attended' %>

<div class="grid-row">
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    <%= step_header %>

    <div class="grid_content_header">
      <h1 class="heading-xlarge gv-u-heading-xxlarge">You haven’t attended a MIAM</h1>
    </div>

    <p class="lede gv-u-text-lede">You’re legally required to attend a
      <abbr title="Mediation Information and Assessment Meeting">MIAM</abbr>, unless you have a valid reason.
    </p>

    <div class=" govuk-govspeak gv-s-prose">
      <p><a href="/miam_exemptions">Check if you have a valid reason</a> before you continue with your application.</p>
    </div>

    <p>If you’re still unsure you can continue and we’ll try and work out if you have a valid reason based on the answers you give.</p>

    <div class="xform-group form-submit">
      <%= link_to 'Confirm and continue', steps_safety_questions_start_path, class: 'button', role: 'button' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
